{"tid":2147360,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"研究指戴罩減輕武肺病情","createTime":"2020-08-09T07:46:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-09T08:02:26.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"dc71d3f8d9a9fe8e14fc90af295d854ffd547e1b","tid":2147360,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T07:46:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200809/AAU4QVKQIGP5YVNOODKT4F36XA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200809%2FAAU4QVKQIGP5YVNOODKT4F36XA%2F&d=SXj%2FfRDdIS6Y9psqMYminNDxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h=cf3ebf8e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200809%2FAAU4QVKQIGP5YVNOODKT4F36XA%2F&h=c338eb06\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200809/AAU4QVKQIGP5YVNOODKT4F36XA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n研究指戴罩減輕武肺病情<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/BKhViaGwhXlHxlk6g7eyR9_cJQM=/640x426/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LADDQQNHJUEUA2OOR7G4XNGXCI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FBKhViaGwhXlHxlk6g7eyR9_cJQM%3D%2F640x426%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLADDQQNHJUEUA2OOR7G4XNGXCI.jpg&h=cfb7e6b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n戴口罩是民眾防範武漢肺炎的基本方法之一。路透社<br />\n<br />\n美國一項研究發現，戴口罩不僅可防止使用者透過飛沬傳播病毒，更可阻截病毒入侵，讓使用者免受感染，即使不幸染病亦有助減輕病情。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n吸入較少病毒粒子<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。她領導的團隊透過動物實驗以及在疫情期間的觀察，歸納出戴口罩的人會吸入較少武漢肺炎病毒粒子，讓免疫系統較容易擊敗入侵病毒。研究將刊登於《一般內科期刊》。<br />\n<br />\n研究員估計武肺患者中有40%人沒有病徵，但當群組中部份人戴口罩，無症狀患者的比例暴增。<span class=\"orange\"><span class=\"x-large\">甘迪以日本的鑽石公主號和阿根廷一艘遊輪為例，前者爆疫時大部份乘客均沒戴口罩，有症狀者高達80%；後者乘客上船時獲發外科口罩，有症狀者低於20%。</span></span>有關數據顯示，戴口罩雖不致讓人免疫，但傾向減輕症狀，有機會減低入院比率及死亡率。<br />\n<br />\n專研空氣傳播的專家馬爾指，基於過去的證據和近日觀察，口罩或可過濾50%或以上的較大顆氣霧，N95效能更佳，布口罩亦有些許效用，指今次研究再為戴口罩提供理據。<br />\n<br />\n美國《紐約時報》"},{"pid":"bf2c3395f0bf774605d88b986d3d7d6b386ea2aa","tid":2147360,"uid":69120,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T07:47:49.000Z","msg":"研究指： 不食飯會感到肚餓"},{"pid":"6ed66a5c427daa3cc12b686c6695bfa330cdaa63","tid":2147360,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T07:54:29.000Z","msg":"歸納出戴口罩的人會吸入較少武漢肺炎病毒粒子，讓免疫系統較容易擊敗入侵病毒"},{"pid":"fe99cc9ae4a9b5e4e1777c961a953394e4bb170f","tid":2147360,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ed66a5c427daa3cc12b686c6695bfa330cdaa63","tid":2147360,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T07:54:29.000Z","msg":"歸納出戴口罩的人會吸入較少武漢肺炎病毒粒子，讓免疫系統較容易擊敗入侵病毒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T07:55:08.000Z","msg":"戴口罩雖不致讓人免疫，但傾向減輕症狀，有機會減低入院比率及死亡率。"},{"pid":"8ae141d8f3c65061bac7806bae6b7b1f5ee1814a","tid":2147360,"uid":245484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T07:56:07.000Z","msg":"研究指山係石頭海係水"},{"pid":"e795942058a10b343b55827bae2d457224a22a04","tid":2147360,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T07:57:11.000Z","msg":"等得研究黎都唔知死左幾多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c37d05d0da0888f70b22e1b6115d5d0f7e452d51","tid":2147360,"uid":302471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T08:02:26.000Z","msg":"研究<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}